Skills.Name: Spirit Blessing
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies within 150 cm of single ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Also grants ongoing HP recovery by <color=red>{1}%</color> of ATK for 10s. Also raises ATK by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 10s. Further raises CRIT ATK by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP, grants ongoing HP recovery, raises ATK and CRIT ATK of all allies within range

Skills.Name: No Escape!
Skills.Description: Inflicts 2-hit DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color>) on single enemy with highest ATK. Inflicts <code=400,param=258><color=#3398f1>Freeze</color> on all enemies within 150 cm of target enemy with highest ATK for 3s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 2-hit DMG on single enemy. Inflicts Freeze on all enemies within range

Skills.Name: Frozen World
Skills.Description: Raises DMG Received for all Red Elemental enemies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>{1}%</color> of ATK. Also raises DMG Inflicted by {3}% multiplied by number of Blue Elementals in party for 15s. Further raises ATK by {6}% multiplied by number of Blue Elementals in party for 15s. Recovers SP of all Blue Elemental allies (except self) by {8}.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises DMG Received for all Red Elemental enemies. Recovers HP of all allies, raises DMG Inflicted and ATK based on number of Blue Elementals in party. Recovers SP of all Blue Elemental allies (except self)

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>5.00%-50.00%</color> according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Ice Spiritual Arts User
Skills.Description: At start of Wave, <code=200,param=115><color=#3398f1>shields</color> DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of all Blue Elemental allies for 60s. Also raises Speed by {1}% for 60s. Further raises Hidden Technique DMG Inflicted by {2}% for 60s.
Skills.ShortDescription: At start of Wave, shields DMG, raises Speed and Hidden Technique DMG Inflicted for all Blue Elemental allies
